{"tid":1792942,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黑警推宣傳片：近日咁亂仲出唔出嚟？唔使擔心，有香港警察「保護」你哋！","createTime":"2019-12-22T04:27:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T05:01:09.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3a840df8b84d2046aaba7fca223df6b019fa7650","tid":1792942,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:27:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/警方推宣傳片-近日咁亂仲出唔出嚟-唔使擔心-有香港警察保護我哋/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%8E%A8%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E7%89%87-%E8%BF%91%E6%97%A5%E5%92%81%E4%BA%82%E4%BB%B2%E5%87%BA%E5%94%94%E5%87%BA%E5%9A%9F-%E5%94%94%E4%BD%BF%E6%93%94%E5%BF%83-%E6%9C%89%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%2F&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3Bdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=d8f40deb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%8E%A8%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E7%89%87-%E8%BF%91%E6%97%A5%E5%92%81%E4%BA%82%E4%BB%B2%E5%87%BA%E5%94%94%E5%87%BA%E5%9A%9F-%E5%94%94%E4%BD%BF%E6%93%94%E5%BF%83-%E6%9C%89%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%2F&h=4759e137\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/警方推宣傳片-近日咁亂仲出唔出嚟-唔使擔心-有香港警察保護我哋/</a><br />\n<br />\n黑警昨晚在facebook 推出宣傳片，剪輯示威者破壞以及近期的衝突片段，每逢12月底，都是與身邊人慶祝佳節的時候，「黑警會繼續守護大家珍而重之的和平。我們與廣大市民一樣，都希望與摰愛親朋共度一個和平、愉快的聖誕佳節。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Untitled-1-02_OWKQF_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FUntitled-1-02_OWKQF_1200x0.png&h=36282987&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑警近日執法手段備受爭議，包括經常在鬧市射催淚彈，以及在商場噴椒等。但黑警在宣傳片當中模擬對話，有人問道，「香港近日咁亂，仲出唔出嚟好呀？」另一人回應，「唔洗擔心，有黑警保護我哋」、「我哋去預祝聖誕節，點會有事發生。」"},{"pid":"4820bce43765e8d0ba172eb004756ba479a18b60","tid":1792942,"uid":2950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d82cc0df568318e396563e9ebc6197925db4807","tid":1792942,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T05:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}